svg.desc: Geoff Ritter's personal logo containing a squared G with rounded corners and an intertwined reversed R on a square background with rounded corners. At the bottom is a bar containing, in all capital letters, the words GEOFF RITTER.

cc:Work.dc:description: Geoff Ritter's personal logo containing a squared G with rounded corners and an intertwined reversed R on a square background with rounded corners. At the bottom is a bar containing, in all capital letters, the words GEOFF RITTER

g.aria-label: Black and white variant must: * Have full rounding on bar * No outline on the logo * Outside stroke on the that is 1/32 the width of the logo. In this design, 8 units thick.
Spacing around logo should equal the 1/8th division
Bar should not appear when logo is smaller than 65px on screen or 0.5 inches in print.
Text is Montserrat and should not appear when logo is smaller than 160px on screen or 1 inch in print.
